Create Google Chrome/Chromium Application Shortcuts on Mac OSX
==========
usage:
ruby ./create_web_application_shortcut.rb <AppName> <AppURL> [AppIconURL]


mesh.js
=========
Layout grid for web page.
Dependency: jquery. 
Usage: 

Mesh.vguide({ left : 50 });
Mesh.vguide({ width : 480 });
Mesh.vguide({ width : 480,  right : 144 });
Mesh.vguide({ right: 50 });
Mesh.hguide({ top: 100 });

Mesh.mesh({
    left: 0,
    right: 0,
    width: 980,
    gutter : 18,
    columns: 12,
    centered : true,
    row: 18,
    order: 3
    });
});


